      "asbval:target_claim_field": "scope",
      "asbval:target_claim_text": "Apply this skill when you have aligned ATAC-seq BAM files and need to detect transcription factor binding sites via footprint analysis. The skill is essential because raw Tn5 insertion signal contains systematic bias toward certain DNA sequences; correction is necessary before sc",
