      "asbval:target_claim_text": "This skill uses TOBIAS BINDetect to classify transcription factor occupancy (bound vs. unbound) at specific genomic locations by comparing corrected ATAC-seq footprint scores and Tn5 insertion depletion patterns across conditions and motif positions.",
