      "asbval:target_claim_field": "scope",
      "asbval:target_claim_text": "Apply this skill after you have (1) corrected ATAC-seq BAM files for Tn5 insertion bias using ATACorrect, (2) computed per-base footprint scores using ScoreBigwig, (3) obtained a motif database (e.g., JASPAR PWMs in TOBIAS-compatible format), and (4) want to infer which TF bindin",
