      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "TOBIAS is a collection of command-line tools utilizing a minimal input of ATAC-seq reads, TF motifs and genome information (Fig. 1b) to perform all levels of footprinting analysis including bias correction (Fig. 1c), footprinting (Fig. 1d), and comparison between conditions (Fig. 1e). Furthermore, TOBIAS includes a variety of auxiliary tools such as TF network inference and visualization of footprints",
